task.summary: Pushing merge of Hardware/Manufacture pages for Adam. New Harware needs debugging still.

Added Software/Vendor pages.
Added functionality on Software license start/end date to only accept software licenses that expire in the future. (Doesn't AJAX refresh on front end, but won't accept in DB).

Added scope forums to software page. Fixed employee phone number / email validation & added hints for formatting validation on front-end (user tips) Working on time remaining functionality for software license tags to display what's left dynamically in the actual status_tag
Added last_updated_by to hardware (need to add to software + fix employee page version of it. Needs method to define it to ensure they can't change the hidden input field - in developement)
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml

Added new index scope to employee page. Added current_account scoped password/confirmation to employee edit page.
Still to do: Authorization for scoped views
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml

Added / working on theme (responsive). Fixed placement with profile link (for some reason broke with new theme but I adjusted) Added profile/user checks for all pages user types in URL (auto redirect with error - works across all lists/views if not authorized) Fixed favicon to appear.
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml

Added check_cost (was not there at all) to software with errors for string characters & only accepts numeric values. Fixed check_cost on hardware with errors for string characters & only accepts numeric values Fixed Custodian Name + Show page title to render name dynamically. Previously showed as empty.
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml

Fixed validation errors with Employee Middle Initial throwing wrong error if blank (now can be blank). Fixed new room / building collection
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml

Cleaned up names on dashboard // added total asset value in its own panel for placeholder
# Conflicts: # .idea/workspace.xml
